children.strValue: Students Read Hacker Monthly For Free

When a few students commented they wouldn't be able to afford Hacker Monthly, I could relate to that - as I was (and I'm sure many of you were) once a student too. So I've been giving away 1 year digital subscription plan to students who emailed about it since.
Today, I'm making it official. If you are still studying in college/university, you get to read Hacker Monthly for free by
submitting your details thru this form
If you feel like giving back, tell your fellow hackers and roommates about this. Thank you.
Hacker Monthly is a print magazine curated from the top articles of Hacker News.
Students Read Hacker Monthly For Free - Hacker Monthly Blog
